This paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it focuses on advancing the state-of-the-art in object detection and 3D pose estimation in the context of robotics. Computer Vision (cs.CV) is also a likely sub-category as the paper deals with generating photorealistic images with accurate 3D pose annotations. Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) are also possible sub-categories as the paper involves the use of synthetic data generation and statistical analysis. Finally, Graphics (cs.GR) is a possible sub-category as the paper mentions the high graphical quality of the backgrounds used in the dataset generation.
